QuestData.Title: Returning from the Pass
QuestData.Description: I still have some cleanup to do here in the pass - there are some mantid still making it through. You're a valuable person to have at hand though, and I know Taran wouldn't appreciate me keeping you longer for such basic work.$B$BTaran should still be in the main camp with Gao-Ran. Report back in. I'll catch up with you a bit later.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report in to Taran Zhu at the Gao-Ran Battlefront.
QuestData.RewardText: Welcome back. I heard about the breaches in the eastern pass. It sounds like I put the right people on the job.
